://www.nme.com/en_au/tag/ps4">PlayStation 4</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/tag/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>上顺序为“下、R1、上、L1、正方形、X、三角形和圆形”，在<a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/tag/xbox-one">Xbox One</a>和 PlayStation 上顺序为“下、RB、上、LB、X、A、Y、B” <a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/tag/xbox-series-xs">Xbox 系列 X|S</a> 。</p><p>如果这些按钮输入成功，游戏会播放短促的铃声效果，解说员会发出吼叫、嘶嘶、吠叫、乌鸦等声音来回应战斗。</p><p>正如<em><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/this-secret-street-fighter-6-code-turns-commentators-into-actual-animals/1100-6516417/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GameSpot</a></em>在其<em>《街头霸王 6》</em>报道中提到的那样，这些按钮与解锁替代颜色的按钮相同，并且两个玩家都可以在超级<a href="https://www.nme.com/brand/nintendo">任天堂</a>娱乐系统的<em>《街头霸王 2》</em>中选择相同角色。</p><p> <em>《街头霸王 6》</em>提供 4 名英语解说员和 4 名日语解说员以及 13 种语言的字幕。前者包括 Jeremy “Vicious” Lopez、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/street-fighter-6-trailer-focuses-on-real-time-commentary-feature-3284543">Steve “TastySteve” Scott、James “jchensor” Chen</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/wwes-zelina-vega-will-be-a-commentator-in-street-fighter-6-3389281">WWE 摔跤手 Thea “Zelina Vega” Trinidad</a> 。 </p><figure id="attachment_3473604" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3473604" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3473604" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/street-fighter-6.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/street-fighter-6.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/street-fighter-6-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/street-fighter-6-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/street-fighter-6-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/street-fighter-6-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/street-fighter-6-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachmen